codex
The strongest pattern is not just single-feature association: `feature_005` has a large positive response-rate association, but that association nearly disappears in several negative-marker strata (`feature_034`, `feature_009`, `feature_065`, and `feature_055`). I’m quantifying those subgroup effects and a compact multivariable interaction model for the final transcript.
